name: PinEnchantedMix By YeiyeiArt
description:
REMEMBER to follow the social networks and ask for your own models (ง͡ ¬᎑¬)ว. This time I bring something different and special, as it's the first checkpoint I'm uploading based on my own style. I noticed that many people liked the LoRa, so I decided to share the complete model with you all so you can experiment and create amazing illustrations with it. The model generates extraordinary images with a unique anime-style. I highly recommend using it with the ControlNet extension and enabling the Color Model; the results are remarkable. ( • ̀ω•́ )✧ Use Clip Skip 2 for better results. Make sure to use popular VAEs like the standard one (vae-ft-mse-840000-ema) to fully exploit the model's potential!! I hope you enjoy it, and don't forget to check out my other models :D

⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️

Don’t forget to check out my other Disney Series Loras on my profile. Currently Rapunzel, Snow White, Merida, Cinderella, Pocahontas, Fa Mulan, Elsa, Anna, Tiana and Alice in Wonderland, Ariel, Aurora, Jasmine From the Princess Series ;D” Also u have The Bonus Series with: Nani Pelekai, Lifeguard (lilo & stitch). And Tinker bell, Jane Porter (Tarzan), Kida (atlantis), Chel, Jessica Rabbit.

Restaurant Series: Ronald McDonald, Wendys

Don’t forget to check out my other Disney Series Loras on my profile. YeiYeiArt.
